Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.72,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Aaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.56,White,,0,0,0,,-(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:21.56,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.84,White,,0,0,0,,-(cossos: es desplomen)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.84,White,,0,0,0,,-(tret)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.20,0:00:46.44,White,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:51.20,White,,0,0,0,,Tu, on t'has pensat que vas?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.60,White,,0,0,0,,No.... no m'ho havíeu dit,\Nque els mataríem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:01:00.52,White,,0,0,0,,Els he avisat que, si no em feien cas, ho pagarien car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:02.80,White,,0,0,0,,S'ho han guanyat a pols.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:06.40,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs..., si és així,\Njo em retiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.68,White,,0,0,0,,Si et retires,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:11.16,White,,0,0,0,,incompliràs el contracte,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.48,White,,0,0,0,,ens trairàs i ho hauràs de pagar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.16,White,,0,0,0,,(home) Ei, vosaltres!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:21.16,White,,0,0,0,,Es pot saber què hi feu, aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:31.04,White,,0,0,0,,(policia: sirena)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"S'aixeca el teló\Ni apareix el protagonista."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:40.00,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Resol els misteris fent\Nuna dansa preciosa."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'operació secreta\Nd'uns delinqüents entre bastidors."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Els descobrirà,\Nla Lliga de Detectius Júnior?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:46.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Amai uso nara tsuiteite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:05.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,Shinjitsu wa setsunaku itai mono DA-KA-RA Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Aimai, my, mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,Isso kimi no subete wo kakete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:17.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,logical na watashi\Nwo damashi nuite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.20,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kitto hajime wa mujaki na koi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:32.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,eforume shite mita dake soushite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:35.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Hikari wo matoi yami ni obieru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,ginmaku sutaa no you ni.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:46.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sou yo kono mama kyokou no sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:53.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,nazo wo tokeba oikakeru\Nriyuu ga nakunaru wa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:03:02.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nani mo kamo omoidoori\Nnante tsumaranai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, lie, lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why? Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:12.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,Itsuwari demo kamawanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:19.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:23.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"En Conan cau per un penya-segat\N(primera part)"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:29.00,White,,0,0,0,,(dona) El delinqüent anomenat\Nel Zorro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:31.56,White,,0,0,0,,ha tornat a cometre\Nun altre robatori amb violència.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:33.56,White,,0,0,0,,Aquesta vegada ha assassinat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.32,White,,0,0,0,,els tres ocupants de la mansió\Non va entrar ahir a robar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.24,White,,0,0,0,,També va ferir de gravetat\Nun agent de policia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.48,White,,0,0,0,,"...que, quan va sentir trets, es\Nva presentar a l'escenari dels fets."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.64,White,,0,0,0,,Com es pot ser tan mesquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:47.48,White,,0,0,0,,Només entra a cases de famosos.\NJa és la quarta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.32,White,,0,0,0,,"...amb una ballesta."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:50.88,White,,0,0,0,,"La policia metropolitana\Nha comunicat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.60,White,,0,0,0,,que dedicarà tots els efectius\Nque facin falta per localitzar-lo."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.64,White,,0,0,0,,No fa gens d'honor al nom del Zorro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.52,White,,0,0,0,,És un assassí cruel i despietat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.36,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Oh... Pare, sisplau.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.24,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Que avui sigui el teu dia lliure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.36,Cyan,,0,0,0,,no vol dir que hagis de començar\Na beure de bon matí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.32,White,,0,0,0,,Ja ho sé, no m'atabalis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.72,White,,0,0,0,,On para, ara, aquell marrec?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.52,White,,0,0,0,,Aquella sangonera,\Nquan sent notícies d'aquestes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.44,White,,0,0,0,,sempre hi ha de dir la seva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:19.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Avui en Conan ha sortit amb l'Ai\Ni amb els altres. No te'n recordes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:22.88,White,,0,0,0,,Esclar. Quina enveja!\NSempre fan el que volen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.88,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Tu, fas enveja.\NTu sí que sempre fas el que vols.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.76,0:04:29.88,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Oh... Quina barra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:34.12,White,,0,0,0,,(Lliga: parla alhora)\NVa, ara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:40.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Macedònia, púding i anguiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:40.64,White,,0,0,0,,Va, Conan, digues què has entès.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.20,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) Correcte.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.40,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Com t'ho has fet,\Nper endevinar-los tots tres?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Tampoc costa tant..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:50.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ara les nostres assignatures\Npreferides.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.12,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Les podria endevinar\Nabans que me les digueu."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.04,White,,0,0,0,,Mireu, ja hi som, ja hem arribat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.16,White,,0,0,0,,(tots) Que bé!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.20,White,,0,0,0,,(Ayumi) Ah! És fantàstic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:07.44,White,,0,0,0,,(Mitsuhiko) I ens hi podrem quedar\Na dormir. Semblarem famosos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.44,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Sí, segur que ens serviran\Nunes anguiles de primera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això ja no ho tinc tan clar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.52,White,,0,0,0,,No, gens ni mica, perquè haurem\Nde cuinar nosaltres mateixos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:19.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ho sento, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.36,White,,0,0,0,,He-he... De veritat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,El que sí que és evident
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,és que el doctor Agasa té contactes amb gent molt important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:29.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,S'ha de ser molt ric\Nper tenir una casa com aquesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.24,White,,0,0,0,,(Genta) Doncs segur\Nque també té algun amic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.40,White,,0,0,0,,que té un restaurant\Nespecialitzat en anguiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.84,White,,0,0,0,,No. Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:38.52,White,,0,0,0,,Tampoc cal\Nque sigui tan contundent...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.84,White,,0,0,0,,Oooh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.52,White,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ayumi! Què passa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.80,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres. Pobre.\NEstà ferit. Qui deu ser?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:00.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Encara és viu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.92,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. Està molt malferit,\Nperò encara respira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.68,White,,0,0,0,,D'acord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Haibara, avisa una ambulància.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.44,White,,0,0,0,,"(ambulància: sirena)"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:14.44,White,,0,0,0,,(sirena)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:35.08,White,,0,0,0,,Quin ensurt, oi, només d'arribar?\NQui devia ser i d'on devia venir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.88,White,,0,0,0,,I què li deu haver passat?\NPotser ho podríem investigar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.88,White,,0,0,0,,Potser només era un lladre\Nque voltava per aquí
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.32,White,,0,0,0,,i, mentre fugia, s'ha entrebancat\Ni s'ha fet mal ell sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.88,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, és possible, però...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:50.92,White,,0,0,0,,s'hauria d'haver disparat ell sol\Namb una ballesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.04,White,,0,0,0,,Una ballesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.48,White,,0,0,0,,-On deu haver anat, en Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:56.48,White,,0,0,0,,-Ara que hi penso...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.92,White,,0,0,0,,Mm? Però si fa un moment era aquí!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Pot ser que li hagi caigut a ell?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Què és això?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.36,White,,0,0,0,,Diria que són noms d'usuari\No contrasenyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.72,White,,0,0,0,,Són molt diferents, totes dues.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:37.00,White,,0,0,0,,Què penses fer? Les entregaràs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:41.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Encara no ho sé. Tu inventa't\Nalguna excusa pels altres.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.12,White,,0,0,0,,Que m'inventi una... excusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Això de la ballesta
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,ha de tenir alguna relació\Namb el robatori d'ahir."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'hi volia preguntar,\Nperò suposo que encara no puc."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:35.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Botes militars?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.64,0:09:14.40,White,,0,0,0,,Però què...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.72,White,,0,0,0,,(cops)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.84,Yellow,,0,0,0,,I ara, a trucar a la policia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:27.40,White,,0,0,0,,(policia: sirena)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:32.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Oh. És l'inspector Megure."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Això vol dir que sí\Nque té relació amb el cas d'ahir."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.28,White,,0,0,0,,(finestra corredissa: s'obre)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Acaba de fugir!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:44.44,White,,0,0,0,,Conan. Què hi fas, aquí?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Conan) Un sospitós ha fugit\Nper la finestra d'aquesta habitació.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.88,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:57.92,White,,0,0,0,,Res. Massa tard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.76,White,,0,0,0,,Havia fugit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:02.04,White,,0,0,0,,He trobat això a les escombraries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.88,Green,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:08.64,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Suposo que això vol dir que el ferit és membre de la banda del Zorro, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.88,0:10:10.64,White,,0,0,0,,De moment hem descobert
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:13.68,White,,0,0,0,,que el Zorro contracta gent diferent\Nper a cada atracament que fa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:18.64,White,,0,0,0,,L'home ferit es diu Yuji Isehara.\NÉs un hacker professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.68,White,,0,0,0,,El nostre departament\Nde ciberdelinqüència
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.60,White,,0,0,0,,feia temps que li anava al darrere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:26.60,White,,0,0,0,,Es dedica a manipular sistemes\Nde seguretat de possibles objectius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.48,White,,0,0,0,,La policia de Kanagawa\Nens ha informat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.32,White,,0,0,0,,que havia aparegut una persona
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:33.08,White,,0,0,0,,que coincidia amb la descripció\Nque tenien del sospitós
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:35.20,White,,0,0,0,,i hem vingut a comprovar-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:38.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Sí. Moltes gràcies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:38.80,White,,0,0,0,,En tens prou, amb aquesta informació?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:42.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ara ja li podré donar\Nun informe complet a en Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:45.28,White,,0,0,0,,Què? Que no troben\Nel senyor Isehara enlloc?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.64,Green,,0,0,0,,També ha desaparegut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.60,White,,0,0,0,,D'acord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.60,Green,,0,0,0,,No pareu fins que el trobeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.52,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Entesos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:08.44,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies per informar-me de tot, inspector. Passi-ho bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.20,Cyan,,0,0,0,,¿Un dels lladres d'ahir ha aparegut
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,a la casa on hi ha en Conan\Ni els altres?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:15.24,White,,0,0,0,,Exacte.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.64,White,,0,0,0,,Es veu que se l'han trobat amagat\Nal jardí. Estava molt malferit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:21.16,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Espero que en Conan... estigui bé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.76,White,,0,0,0,,Hi ha l'inspector, dona.\NNo cal que pateixis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:28.44,White,,0,0,0,,Mm... Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:28.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Ja, però això no vol dir res.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per sort, n'he fet una foto\Ni me l'he guardat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:53.28,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare, et penses passar tot el dia bevent, o què?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.48,White,,0,0,0,,Què?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.48,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Va, anem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:59.24,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No et deus pensar que en Conan es quedarà allà assegut sense fer res.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Coneixent-lo, ja deu estar fent\Nalguna cosa perillosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.88,White,,0,0,0,,Però què dius, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.28,White,,0,0,0,,L'inspector no m'ha demanat\Nque em fes càrrec del cas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.44,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare, què et dic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:09.44,White,,0,0,0,,No hi penso anar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:11.88,White,,0,0,0,,El gran detectiu Kogoro Mouri\Nno té cap necessitat de...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.72,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.72,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Que t'aixequis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.80,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaaaaaai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.80,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Au, vinga, anem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Hi soc molt a prop."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:36.40,White,,0,0,0,,Quina barra que té! No hi ha dret.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:40.12,White,,0,0,0,,Si ha descobert alguna cosa,\Nens ho hauria d'haver dit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:43.96,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. La Lliga de Detectius Júnior som tots, no és ell sol.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.08,White,,0,0,0,,Doncs jo el que tinc és molta gana.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:13.48,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres. Ja no el veig.\NOn es deu haver ficat, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:17.68,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. Que estrany, oi?\NFins fa un moment encara el vèiem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:20.32,White,,0,0,0,,Ostres, ja comença a fer-se fosc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.36,White,,0,0,0,,I si li ha passat... alguna cosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.68,White,,0,0,0,,Hauríem de pensar en nosaltres.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.56,White,,0,0,0,,Què? Què vols dir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:31.84,White,,0,0,0,,Sí. És veritat.\NEm fa l'efecte que ens hem perdut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.00,White,,0,0,0,,No m'ho diguis, això.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:37.88,White,,0,0,0,,No em diguis que ens quedarem\Nsense sopar. Jo vull sopar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.88,White,,0,0,0,,Mireu, si el sol es pon per allà,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:44.40,White,,0,0,0,,és que el mar és cap allà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.48,White,,0,0,0,,De moment, jo sabria trobar\Nel camí perfectament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:49.96,White,,0,0,0,,I encara tenim una estona de marge per tornar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Ostres, ets la millor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:53.24,White,,0,0,0,,-Ho dius de veritat, Ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:56.32,White,,0,0,0,,-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:56.32,White,,0,0,0,,-Així, no ens quedarem sense sopar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.64,White,,0,0,0,,Però abans\Nprovem d'anar una mica més enllà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No tinc clar que sigui per aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ja no sé on soc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:07.80,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però... si el sol es pon per allà,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,vol dir que el mar és cap allà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què és això?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.72,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Acabo d'entrar en una cova.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.48,White,,0,0,0,,(onatge: brogit)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:23.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Brisa marina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:26.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Això vol dir...\Nque hi ha d'haver una sortida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,No, per aquí no puc sortir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:41.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Quina passada! És impressionant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Però...\Nno m'hauria d'entretenir més.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:55.96,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per fi he sortit de la cova,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.28,Yellow,,0,0,0,,però ara ja és massa fosc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.44,Yellow,,0,0,0,,M'he tornat a perdre?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Val més que torni enrere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:18.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Què és allò?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,L'he trobat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.24,White,,0,0,0,,-(trencadissa)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.24,White,,0,0,0,,-(cop)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.60,White,,0,0,0,,Mira que ets idiota.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.36,White,,0,0,0,,Què, Zorro, què en fem, ara?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.96,White,,0,0,0,,Et conec massa bé, Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.80,White,,0,0,0,,Sabia perfectament que vindries aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:17.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"És ell."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.88,White,,0,0,0,,No... no em matis, sisplau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.88,White,,0,0,0,,T'ho suplico. No em matis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.84,White,,0,0,0,,Per la teva dona i pel teu fill?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.92,White,,0,0,0,,No siguis tan melodramàtic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.76,White,,0,0,0,,Suposo que has parlat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.68,White,,0,0,0,,No. No he dit res.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:39.72,White,,0,0,0,,Et deixaré triar, doncs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.68,White,,0,0,0,,O em desempallego\Nde la teva dona i del teu fill,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.16,White,,0,0,0,,o tu mateix acabes amb la teva vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.56,White,,0,0,0,,Què t'estimes més?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.40,0:16:52.32,White,,0,0,0,,Tria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.96,White,,0,0,0,,Qui hi ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:40.20,White,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.76,White,,0,0,0,,Qui ets, tu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.76,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Per aquí, de pressa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,En Conan Edogawa, un detectiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:53.16,White,,0,0,0,,-(Zorro) On és?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:53.16,White,,0,0,0,,-Un... un detectiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:55.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,De pressa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:17:59.16,White,,0,0,0,,Era un nen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.96,White,,0,0,0,,Punyeta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.16,White,,0,0,0,,On carai s'han ficat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Xxt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:21.36,White,,0,0,0,,Em... em volen matar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:25.08,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Estigui tranquil.\NDe moment no tenen ni idea d'on som.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.52,White,,0,0,0,,Aah! No vull morir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.00,White,,0,0,0,,Per aquí.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.40,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Esperi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Ostres.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.48,White,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Què? En Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.80,White,,0,0,0,,-Oh... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:34.84,White,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:43.80,White,,0,0,0,,(Kogoro) Una altra cervesa.\NNo, dues...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:47.68,Cyan,,0,0,0,,No sé per què,\Nperò tinc un mal pressentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:49.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pot córrer una mica més, sisplau?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:56.00,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Pare, desperta't d'una vegada, va.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.08,White,,0,0,0,,No. No em mateu. Sisplau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:05.20,White,,0,0,0,,Després de tots els problemes\Nque ens has portat,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.12,White,,0,0,0,,moriràs com un traïdor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.36,White,,0,0,0,,Adeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.04,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:31.36,White,,0,0,0,,(criden)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.96,White,,0,0,0,,-Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.64,White,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.56,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaaah! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.44,White,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:52.92,White,,0,0,0,,Ah, hola, doctor Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.84,White,,0,0,0,,Mira quin detall,\Nha sortit a rebre'ns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.28,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Els hi ha passat alguna cosa\Na en Conan i els nens, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:04.12,White,,0,0,0,,Sí, m'acaben de trucar els nens\Ndient-me que en Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.96,White,,0,0,0,,Què? No pot ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.96,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què ha dit? Que... que en Conan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.84,White,,0,0,0,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.84,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaaaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.16,White,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:28.24,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to nara\Nitsumade mo yume wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:34.36,Songs,,0,0,0,,aruite yukitai to negau.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:43.60,Songs,,0,0,0,,Nee tatoeba juunen mirai no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:50.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,bokura wa dou shiteiru ka na.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:54.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Yume no meiro nuke
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:56.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,doa no soto kimi ga ite
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:58.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,waratteru ka na.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.68,0:22:05.40,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kimi to nara\Nitsumade mo yume wo mite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:11.28,Songs,,0,0,0,,aruite yukitai to negau.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:16.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ima mo boku wa yume no naka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:24.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oikakete oikakete doko made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:28.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,mada minu keshiki wo mezasu yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:30.80,Songs,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:37.64,Songs,,0,0,0,,Sore ga boku no yume\Nkimi to zutto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:39.24,White,,0,0,0,,En Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.72,0:22:41.36,White,,0,0,0,,No pot ser de cap manera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:43.76,White,,0,0,0,,Però... ho hem vist,\Nels ulls no enganyen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:47.68,White,,0,0,0,,Gràcies, inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.08,0:22:47.68,Green,,0,0,0,,No ho penso permetre de cap manera.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:50.56,Cyan,,0,0,0,,Què? L'Ai també ha desaparegut?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:53.88,White,,0,0,0,,He vingut sola,\Ntal com m'heu demanat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:57.84,White,,0,0,0,,Som-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:02.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"No us perdeu el pròxim episodi:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:05.92,Yellow,,0,0,0,,'En Conan cau per un penya-segat\N(segona part)'"
